Moreover, these invoices were found during the search carried out in the office of <0xC3><0x81>rpád Kemecsei, at the Ministry of Education.
At the hearing, a portion of the defendants will report on the method of making the invoices, as they had done before the Prosecutor's Office previously.
What might be really interesting would be that the main accused, János Zuschlag himself, decides to lift the veil over the whole story.
